## Skills

Reusable agent skills live under `skills/` (or `$AGENT_OS_SOURCE/skills/` in thin-client mode). Each skill is a subfolder containing a `skill.md` file.

**Available skills:**

| Skill | Folder | Purpose |
|-------|--------|---------|
| deploy-files | `skills/deploy-files/` | Deploy Business OS files into target project (fat-client) |
| deploy-repo | `skills/deploy-repo/` | Full repo deploy (clone or archive) |
| deploy-basic | `skills/deploy-basic/` | Thin-client bootstrap — copies `.cursorrules` (with `AGENT_OS_SOURCE` pointer) + `.work.biz/` skeleton; skills resolve from source at runtime. `@deploy-basic`, `@deploy-basic update`, `@deploy-basic status` |
| biz-bootstrap | `skills/biz-bootstrap/` | Scaffold `.work.biz/`, `.cursorrules` from templates |
| biz-strategy | `skills/biz-strategy/` | Niche, offer, positioning, target buyer |
| biz-brand | `skills/biz-brand/` | LinkedIn, website, brand presence |
| biz-pricing | `skills/biz-pricing/` | Value-based pricing framework |
| biz-content | `skills/biz-content/` | Content publishing and strategy |
| biz-community | `skills/biz-community/` | Community engagement playbook |
| biz-referrals | `skills/biz-referrals/` | Systematic referral generation |
| biz-discovery | `skills/biz-discovery/` | Sales discovery calls |
| biz-proposal | `skills/biz-proposal/` | Proposal writing and scoping |
| biz-objections | `skills/biz-objections/` | Handle sales objections |
| biz-review | `skills/biz-review/` | Weekly/quarterly business review |
| biz-market-validate | `skills/biz-market-validate/` | Test offers before committing |
| biz-pipeline-diagnosis | `skills/biz-pipeline-diagnosis/` | Find and fix funnel bottlenecks |
| session-biz | `skills/session-biz/` | Session open/close; HANDOFF, NEXT; `context` read-only load + uncommitted-aware. Aliased as `session-control` (`@session-control context`, `@session-control start`, etc.) |
| biz-director | `skills/biz-director/` | Universal orchestrator; free-text → skill routing |
| content-writing | `skills/content-writing/` | Craft of writing articles, posts, case studies, landing pages, emails (project-aware) |
| business-ideas | `skills/business-ideas/` | Structured, stress-tested business/venture idea generation |
| product-service-ideas | `skills/product-service-ideas/` | Buildable, stack-fit product/service concept generation + MVP scoping |
| biz-project-query-setup | `skills/biz-project-query-setup/` | Optional. Guide through tools-project API key, MCP registration, connectivity test. OS-aware (tailors guidance per framework). |

**Usage:** When a task matches a skill's purpose, read `skill.md` and follow the workflow.

